The Study

This is the Oracle's study. A big resolute desk dominates the room. On the desk is a laptop and piles of papers. A mahogany chair is by the desk. There are several shelves containing his journals. On one corner of the room is a spiral staircase leading up. Near the desk on the floor is some red shrapnel looking like glass. You can go up to the tower and east to the hall.
