The Grassy Path

You are on a grassy path between thick bushes. You can go south to the backyard of Mansion Ratakim or northeast to a gravel road.
> northeast

> northeast
When you reach the end of the path you see a small woman dressed in pink trying to reach something on a traffic sign.

 "Oh how I hate these T 1,5:s! They are the worst!" She orders her black dog to stay still by the sign and climbs on the beast. You can't quite see what she is doing but after a few seconds she steps back down.

 You approach her and she startles. "Just walking my dog here." she says and continues "I am Sara Thirdofsmallbay and this here is Dummy." You start to introduce yourself but she cuts in "Now I must go to work but before that I have to go to a junkyard to get some spare parts for three BMW:s and I have a meet in twenty minutes in Bay City...." Her phone beeps "Oh another new cache...bye now, I must fly, literally!" She starts running west along the road. The dog looks apologetically at you and then follows her.

 You look after them not sure what to make of this.

