You climb to the summit a little sweaty and get startled by an ugly beast on the top. You have never seen anything like it. It's like half human, half dog or wolf or something. It growls at you and drool is dripping between it's sharp teeth. "We order you to go back down! This is our place now. No humans allowed!". For a brief second you wonder what "we"? The beast is alone.

The Top of the Goblin Mountain

You are at the summit of the Goblin Mountain. A beautiful view lies in every direction, lakes and forests. There is a cave entrance to west and you can also go down along a path to southwest. There is a threatening, ill-mannered Nameless Beast here. Half human, half canine. It blocks your way to the cave.
> give can of spiced dog food to beast

> give can of spiced dog food to beast
The beast takes the can and smells it suspiciously. It then starts devouring it ranting: "We are hungry, we are soooo hungry!". After finishing the food it holds it's stomach. "What did you do to us? Oh you petty human, what did you do to us?" You can see a stream of diarrhea running down it's hairy legs.
"Oh how we hurt! We shall get you for this!" The beast starts running down the path when suddenly Hellcat jumps from a cliff on it's head starting to claw at it's eyes. From somewhere in your mind comes lyrics of an Offspring song and you sing after it: "Now dance, fucker, dance, man, he never had a chance!".
