The Courtyard

High walls rise to north, west and south. There is a big gate in the western wall leading outside. To east is a door to a two-story mansion. Above the door is a sign. A tower rises from the roof of the mansion at one corner. There are some flowerbeds here and a bench. The Oracle sits on the bench and a big tomcat sleeps in his lap. There are a few empty beer cans on the ground beside them.
> give pill to oracle

> give pill to oracle
The Oracle takes the pill, looks at it and says "Viagra!". He then swallows it. You can see his eyes start to focus and it looks like at least twenty years are lifted off him. "I guess I have you to thank for this! Now there is an important phone call I have to make, but don't go anywhere, we have some unfinished business." He takes his phone out and walks away from you to talk in privacy. He makes a call and you can see tears in his eyes. After finishing the call he comes back to you.

The Oracle wipes the tears from his eyes and says "She is coming home! I can't thank you enough! Or actually I can, I will give you access to my most secret journal. When you find it you'll need a SECRET WORD. It's the TITLE of the most famous fan-fiction taking place in the Ready Player One universe. You can google it. And by coincidence it's also an anagram of what I'm called."

You sit side by side on the bench waiting for Mrs Muggle to come home and have a few beers. The Oracle tells you about his life and you are amazed by how much he has experienced. The cat jumps on your lap and purrs. You can see that he is wearing a collar with a tag. There is a code on the tag: 7PK8DG.

Mrs Muggle arrives and the Oracle stands up. "I'll deal with you later, mister!" she says and faces you. "I understand that you are responsible for getting him back to his senses. I'm very grateful! He can be a pain in the ass but I love him and I missed him very much!" She hugs you and gives you a kiss on the cheek. They both bid you farewell and let you out of the gate.

The End

You are outside the gate leading to Mansion Ratakim. When you look back you can see the Oracle and Mrs Muggle hugging and kissing each other. They are both crying. The cat is at their feet and when you look at him he winks at you.

One thing is bothering you: the Commodore 64 in the shelter under the mansion, and especially the floppy disk drive! You have seen it somewhere before, but WHERE? When you find it, you can zoom in the picture to be sure. Then all you have to do is to give the checker the CODE.

The only way you can go is west towards the cache ;).

Thank you very much for playing my game! I hope you enjoyed!
PS. Remember the Oracle's words about the SECRET WORD at the cache and please be careful with it.
